        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif text-[#8d6e63] mb-8">
          Blooming Ideas for Your Garden Journey
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#795548] max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Discover whimsical and organic gardening tips at Blossom & Brew. From planting blooms to brewing natural remedies, our guides will inspire your floral journey.
