        Join our community of gardeners and start your floral journey today!
      </p>
      <button class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#f4c2c2] font-bold text-lg rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-[#fff8e1] transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
        Get Started
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes float {
    0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
  }
  
  .animate-float {
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .delay-100 {
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
  }
  
  .delay-300 {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }
</style>